726741f-a.title: Queens: Furmanville Avenue - 83rd Street
726741f-a.text:
Furmanville Avenue, adjoining the S.E. corner of
83rd Street. The house was the property of one Schwarz
in 1891 and was owned by Henry Bottjer in 1909. Furman-
ville Avenue was known as Middle Village Road and Juniper
Swamp Road.
July 1, 1940
P. L. Sperr
NO REPRODUCTIONS
